    "The statistically significant metrics where the confidence intervals don't overlap are shown in bold.",
    "DeepCoro predictions were binarized with a threshold of 0.23, as determined on the validation set, and clinical used a threshold of 0.7 for sever stenosis classification.",
    "The range in parentheses is the 95% confidence interval generated by bootstrapping.",
    "Area Under the Precision-Recall Curve, AUROC Area Under the Receiver Operating Curve, MAE Mean Absolute Error, r Pearson's correlation coefficient, RCA Right Coronary Artery, LCA Left Coronary Artery.",
